Class createHotelModel

java.lang.Object
createHotelModel
public class createHotelModel extends Object
This class represents the model for creating and managing hotels. It provides methods to initialize room details and help create new hotel instances.

      public Hotel createHotel(String name, int standardRooms, int deluxeRooms, int executiveRooms, hotelGuiView gui)

      Parameters:
      name - the name of the hotel
      standardRooms - the number of standard rooms
      deluxeRooms - the number of deluxe rooms
      executiveRooms - the number of executive rooms
      gui - the GUI view to interact with for validation
